  "title": "Crisp Chinese Beef Kidney One-Pot",
  "description": "A delicious and easy-to-make one-pot dish from Yunnan, China featuring beef kidney with a hint of yuzu-cure. Pungent and crisp, it's a great option for flexitarian diets.",
